{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.1","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:1","prev_osis_id":"Gen.040.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-36: cf. Ge 40. Da 2 et 4. La 3:26.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Au bout de deux ans, Pharaon eut un songe. Voici, il se tenait pr\u00e8s du fleuve.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.2","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:2","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.40.23","name":"Gen\u00e8se 40:23","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.40.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.2","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:2","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Et voici, sept vaches belles \u00e0 voir et grasses de chair mont\u00e8rent hors du fleuve, et se mirent \u00e0 pa\u00eetre dans la prairie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.3","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:3","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.1","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:1","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.3","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:3","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Sept autres vaches laides \u00e0 voir et maigres de chair mont\u00e8rent derri\u00e8re elles hors du fleuve, et se tinrent \u00e0 leurs c\u00f4t\u00e9s sur le bord du fleuve.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.4","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:4","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.2","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:2","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.4","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:4","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Les vaches laides \u00e0 voir et maigres de chair mang\u00e8rent les sept vaches belles \u00e0 voir et grasses de chair. Et Pharaon s\u2019\u00e9veilla.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.5","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:5","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.3","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:3","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.5","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:5","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Il se rendormit, et il eut un second songe. Voici, sept \u00e9pis gras et beaux mont\u00e8rent sur une m\u00eame tige.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.6","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:6","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.4","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:4","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.6","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:6","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Et sept \u00e9pis maigres et br\u00fbl\u00e9s par le vent d\u2019orient pouss\u00e8rent apr\u00e8s eux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.7","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:7","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.5","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:5","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.7","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:7","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Les \u00e9pis maigres engloutirent les sept \u00e9pis gras et pleins. Et Pharaon s\u2019\u00e9veilla. Voil\u00e0 le songe.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.8","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:8","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.6","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:6","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.8","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:8","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Le matin, Pharaon eut l\u2019esprit agit\u00e9, et il fit appeler tous les magiciens et tous les sages de l\u2019\u00c9gypte. Il leur raconta ses songes. Mais personne ne put les expliquer \u00e0 Pharaon.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.9","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:9","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.7","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:7","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.9","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:9","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Alors le chef des \u00e9chansons prit la parole, et dit \u00e0 Pharaon: Je vais rappeler aujourd\u2019hui le souvenir de ma faute.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.10","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:10","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.8","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:8","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.10","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:10","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Pharaon s\u2019\u00e9tait irrit\u00e9 contre ses serviteurs; et il m\u2019avait fait mettre en prison dans la maison du chef des gardes, moi et le chef des panetiers.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.11","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:11","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.9","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:9","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.11","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:11","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Nous e\u00fbmes l\u2019un et l\u2019autre un songe dans une m\u00eame nuit; et chacun de nous re\u00e7ut une explication en rapport avec le songe qu\u2019il avait eu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.12","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:12","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.10","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:10","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.12","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:12","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Il y avait l\u00e0 avec nous un jeune H\u00e9breu, esclave du chef des gardes. Nous lui racont\u00e2mes nos songes, et il nous les expliqua.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.13","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:13","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.11","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:11","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.13","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:13","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Les choses sont arriv\u00e9es selon l\u2019explication qu\u2019il nous avait donn\u00e9e. Pharaon me r\u00e9tablit dans ma charge, et il fit pendre le chef des panetiers.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.14","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:14","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.12","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:12","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.14","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:14","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Pharaon fit appeler Joseph. On le fit sortir en h\u00e2te de prison. Il se rasa, changea de v\u00eatements, et se rendit vers Pharaon.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.15","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:15","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.13","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:13","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.15","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:15","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Pharaon dit \u00e0 Joseph: J\u2019ai eu un songe. Personne ne peut l\u2019expliquer; et j\u2019ai appris que tu expliques un songe, apr\u00e8s l\u2019avoir entendu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.16","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:16","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.14","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:14","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.16","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:16","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Joseph r\u00e9pondit \u00e0 Pharaon, en disant: Ce n\u2019est pas moi! C\u2019est Dieu qui donnera une r\u00e9ponse favorable \u00e0 Pharaon.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.17","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:17","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.15","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:15","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.17","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:17","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Pharaon dit alors \u00e0 Joseph: Dans mon songe, voici, je me tenais sur le bord du fleuve.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.18","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:18","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.16","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:16","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.18","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:18","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Et voici, sept vaches grasses de chair et belles d\u2019apparence mont\u00e8rent hors du fleuve, et se mirent \u00e0 pa\u00eetre dans la prairie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.19","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:19","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.17","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:17","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.19","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:19","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Sept autres vaches mont\u00e8rent derri\u00e8re elles, maigres, fort laides d\u2019apparence, et d\u00e9charn\u00e9es: je n\u2019en ai point vu d\u2019aussi laides dans tout le pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.20","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:20","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.18","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:18","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.20","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:20","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Les vaches d\u00e9charn\u00e9es et laides mang\u00e8rent les sept premi\u00e8res vaches qui \u00e9taient grasses.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.21","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:21","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.19","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:19","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.21","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:21","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Elles les engloutirent dans leur ventre, sans qu\u2019on s\u2019aper\u00e7\u00fbt qu\u2019elles y fussent entr\u00e9es; et leur apparence \u00e9tait laide comme auparavant. Et je m\u2019\u00e9veillai.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.22","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:22","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.20","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:20","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.22","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:22","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Je vis encore en songe sept \u00e9pis pleins et beaux, qui mont\u00e8rent sur une m\u00eame tige.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.23","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:23","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.21","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:21","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.23","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:23","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Et sept \u00e9pis vides, maigres, br\u00fbl\u00e9s par le vent d\u2019orient, pouss\u00e8rent apr\u00e8s eux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.24","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:24","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.22","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:22","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.24","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:24","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Les \u00e9pis maigres engloutirent les sept beaux \u00e9pis. Je l\u2019ai dit aux magiciens, mais personne ne m\u2019a donn\u00e9 l\u2019explication.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.25","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:25","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.23","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:23","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.25","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:25","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Joseph dit \u00e0 Pharaon: Ce qu\u2019a song\u00e9 Pharaon est une seule chose; Dieu a fait conna\u00eetre \u00e0 Pharaon ce qu\u2019il va faire.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.26","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:26","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.24","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:24","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.26","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:26","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Les sept vaches belles sont sept ann\u00e9es: et les sept \u00e9pis beaux sont sept ann\u00e9es: c\u2019est un seul songe.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.27","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:27","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.25","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:25","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.27","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:27","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Les sept vaches d\u00e9charn\u00e9es et laides, qui montaient derri\u00e8re les premi\u00e8res, sont sept ann\u00e9es; et les sept \u00e9pis vides, br\u00fbl\u00e9s par le vent d\u2019orient, seront sept ann\u00e9es de famine.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.28","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:28","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.26","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:26","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.28","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:28","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Ainsi, comme je viens de le dire \u00e0 Pharaon, Dieu a fait conna\u00eetre \u00e0 Pharaon ce qu\u2019il va faire.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.29","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:29","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.27","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:27","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.29","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:29","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Voici, il y aura sept ann\u00e9es de grande abondance dans tout le pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.30","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:30","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.28","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:28","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.30","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:30","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Sept ann\u00e9es de famine viendront apr\u00e8s elles; et l\u2019on oubliera toute cette abondance au pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte, et la famine consumera le pays.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.31","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:31","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.29","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:29","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.31","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:31","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Cette famine qui suivra sera si forte qu\u2019on ne s\u2019apercevra plus de l\u2019abondance dans le pays.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.32","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:32","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.30","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:30","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.32","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:32","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Si Pharaon a vu le songe se r\u00e9p\u00e9ter une seconde fois, c\u2019est que la chose est arr\u00eat\u00e9e de la part de Dieu, et que Dieu se h\u00e2tera de l\u2019ex\u00e9cuter.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.33","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:33","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.31","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:31","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.33","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:33","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>Maintenant, que Pharaon choisisse un homme intelligent et sage, et qu\u2019il le mette \u00e0 la t\u00eate du pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.32","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:32","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.34","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:34","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>Que Pharaon \u00e9tablisse des commissaires sur le pays, pour lever un cinqui\u00e8me des r\u00e9coltes de l\u2019\u00c9gypte pendant les sept ann\u00e9es d\u2019abondance.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.35","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:35","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.33","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:33","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.35","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:35","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.036,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup>Qu\u2019ils rassemblent tous les produits de ces bonnes ann\u00e9es qui vont venir; qu\u2019ils fassent, sous l\u2019autorit\u00e9 de Pharaon, des amas de bl\u00e9, des approvisionnements dans les villes, et qu\u2019ils en aient la garde.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.36","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:36","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.34","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:34","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.36","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:36","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.037,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup>Ces provisions seront en r\u00e9serve pour le pays, pour les sept ann\u00e9es de famine qui arriveront dans le pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte, afin que le pays ne soit pas consum\u00e9 par la famine.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.37","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:37","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.37"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.35","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:35","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"37","lastverse":"37","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.37","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.37","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:37","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.038,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 37-49: cf. (Ps 105:17-22; 113:7, 8. Ac 7:9, 10. Ge 45:4-8.) Ph 2:9-11.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.37\" class=\"v\">37<\/sup>\n    Ces paroles plurent \u00e0 Pharaon et \u00e0 tous ses serviteurs.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.38","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:38","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.38"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.36","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:36","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"38","lastverse":"38","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.38","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.38","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:38","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.037,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.039,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.38\" class=\"v\">38<\/sup>Et Pharaon dit \u00e0 ses serviteurs: Trouverions-nous un homme comme celui-ci, ayant en lui l\u2019esprit de Dieu?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.39","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:39","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.39"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.37","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:37","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.37"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"39","lastverse":"39","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.39","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.39","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:39","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.038,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.040,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.39\" class=\"v\">39<\/sup>Et Pharaon dit \u00e0 Joseph: Puisque Dieu t\u2019a fait conna\u00eetre toutes ces choses, il n\u2019y a personne qui soit aussi intelligent et aussi sage que toi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.40","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:40","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.40"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.38","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:38","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.38"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"40","lastverse":"40","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.40","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.40","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:40","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.039,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.041,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.40\" class=\"v\">40<\/sup>Je t\u2019\u00e9tablis sur ma maison, et tout mon peuple ob\u00e9ira \u00e0 tes ordres. Le tr\u00f4ne seul m\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8vera au-dessus de toi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.41"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.39","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:39","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.39"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"41","lastverse":"41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.41","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.41","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:41","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.040,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.042,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.41\" class=\"v\">41<\/sup>Pharaon dit \u00e0 Joseph: Vois, je te donne le commandement de tout le pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.42"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.40","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:40","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.40"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"42","lastverse":"42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.42","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.42","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:42","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.041,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.043,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.42\" class=\"v\">42<\/sup>Pharaon \u00f4ta son anneau de la main, et le mit \u00e0 la main de Joseph; il le rev\u00eatit d\u2019habits de fin lin, et lui mit un collier d\u2019or au cou.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.43","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:43","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.43"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.41"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"43","lastverse":"43","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.43","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.43","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:43","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.042,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.044,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.43\" class=\"v\">43<\/sup>Il le fit monter sur le char qui suivait le sien; et l\u2019on criait devant lui: A genoux! C\u2019est ainsi que Pharaon lui donna le commandement de tout le pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.44","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:44","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.44"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.42","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:42","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.42"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"44","lastverse":"44","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.44","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.44","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:44","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.043,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.045,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.44\" class=\"v\">44<\/sup>Il dit encore \u00e0 Joseph: Je suis Pharaon! Et sans toi personne ne l\u00e8vera la main ni le pied dans tout le pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.45","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:45","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.45"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.43","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:43","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.43"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"45","lastverse":"45","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.45","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.45","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:45","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.044,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.046,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.45\" class=\"v\">45<\/sup>Pharaon appela Joseph du nom de Tsaphnath-Paen\u00e9ach; et il lui donna pour femme Asnath, fille de Poti-Ph\u00e9ra, pr\u00eatre d\u2019On. Et Joseph partit pour visiter le pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.46","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:46","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.46"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.44","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:44","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.44"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"46","lastverse":"46","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.46","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.46","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:46","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.045,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.047,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.46\" class=\"v\">46<\/sup>Joseph \u00e9tait \u00e2g\u00e9 de trente ans lorsqu\u2019il se pr\u00e9senta devant Pharaon, roi d\u2019\u00c9gypte; et il quitta Pharaon, et parcourut tout le pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.47","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:47","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.47"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.45","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:45","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.45"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"47","lastverse":"47","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.47","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.47","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:47","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.046,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.048,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.47\" class=\"v\">47<\/sup>Pendant les sept ann\u00e9es de fertilit\u00e9, la terre rapporta abondamment.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.48","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:48","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.48"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.46","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:46","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.46"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"48","lastverse":"48","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.48","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.48","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:48","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.047,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.049,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.48\" class=\"v\">48<\/sup>Joseph rassembla tous les produits de ces sept ann\u00e9es dans le pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte; il fit des approvisionnements dans les villes, mettant dans l\u2019int\u00e9rieur de chaque ville les productions des champs d\u2019alentour.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.49","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:49","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.49"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.47","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:47","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.47"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"49","lastverse":"49","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.49","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.49","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:49","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.048,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.050,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.49\" class=\"v\">49<\/sup>Joseph amassa du bl\u00e9, comme le sable de la mer, en quantit\u00e9 si consid\u00e9rable que l\u2019on cessa de compter, parce qu\u2019il n\u2019y avait plus de nombre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.50","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:50","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.50"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.48","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:48","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.48"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"50","lastverse":"50","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.50","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.50","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:50","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.049,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.051,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 50-57: cf. Ge 48; 47:13-26.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.50\" class=\"v\">50<\/sup>Avant les ann\u00e9es de famine, il naquit \u00e0 Joseph deux fils, que lui enfanta Asnath, fille de Poti-Ph\u00e9ra, pr\u00eatre d\u2019On.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.51","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:51","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.51"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.49","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:49","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.49"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"51","lastverse":"51","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.51","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.51","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:51","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.050,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.052,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.51\" class=\"v\">51<\/sup>Joseph donna au premier-n\u00e9 le nom de Manass\u00e9, car, dit-il, Dieu m\u2019a fait oublier toutes mes peines et toute la maison de mon p\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.52","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:52","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.52"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.50","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:50","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.50"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"52","lastverse":"52","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.52","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.52","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:52","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.051,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.053,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.52\" class=\"v\">52<\/sup>Et il donna au second le nom d\u2019\u00c9phra\u00efm, car, dit-il, Dieu m\u2019a rendu f\u00e9cond dans le pays de mon affliction.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.53","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:53","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.53"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.51","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:51","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.51"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"53","lastverse":"53","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.53","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.53","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:53","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.052,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.054,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.53\" class=\"v\">53<\/sup>Les sept ann\u00e9es d\u2019abondance qu\u2019il y eut au pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte s\u2019\u00e9coul\u00e8rent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.54","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:54","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.54"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.52","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:52","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.52"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"54","lastverse":"54","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.54","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.54","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:54","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.053,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.055,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.54\" class=\"v\">54<\/sup>Et les sept ann\u00e9es de famine commenc\u00e8rent \u00e0 venir, ainsi que Joseph l\u2019avait annonc\u00e9. Il y eut famine dans tous les pays; mais dans tout le pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte il y avait du pain.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.55","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:55","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.55"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.53","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:53","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.53"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"55","lastverse":"55","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.55","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.55","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:55","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.054,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.056,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.55\" class=\"v\">55<\/sup>Quand tout le pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte fut aussi affam\u00e9, le peuple cria \u00e0 Pharaon pour avoir du pain. Pharaon dit \u00e0 tous les \u00c9gyptiens: Allez vers Joseph, et faites ce qu\u2019il vous dira.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.56","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:56","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.56"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.54","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:54","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.54"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"56","lastverse":"56","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.56","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.56","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:56","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.055,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.041.057,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.56\" class=\"v\">56<\/sup>La famine r\u00e9gnait dans tout le pays. Joseph ouvrit tous les lieux d\u2019approvisionnements, et vendit du bl\u00e9 aux \u00c9gyptiens. La famine augmentait dans le pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.57","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:57","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.57"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.55","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:55","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.55"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"57","lastverse":"57","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.57","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.57","label":"","reference":"Gen\u00e8se 41:57","prev_osis_id":"Gen.041.056,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Gen.042.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Gen.41.57\" class=\"v\">57<\/sup>Et de tous les pays on arrivait en \u00c9gypte, pour acheter du bl\u00e9 aupr\u00e8s de Joseph; car la famine \u00e9tait forte dans tous les pays.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Gen.41","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.42.1","name":"Gen\u00e8se 42:1","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.42.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Gen.41.56","name":"Gen\u00e8se 41:56","id":"fra-LSG:Gen.41.56"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81e88afe231.95701402');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81e88afe231.95701402\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81e88afe231.95701402","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81e88afe231.95701402'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81e88afe231.95701402\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}